reviewText: I've ALWAYS liked this show & MOST of the cast members,the only one I didn't really care for was Tara,she was so damn angry,sarcastic,rude & needy,but her cousin Lafayette was the BEST! R.I.P Nelson Ellis,you will be missed
Was not the Complete First Season.  Only received disc two.

This is truly one of my favorite shows. Vampires, Werewolves & Shape-Shifters, among others. I love me some Lafayette, Alcide, Pam & Eric. I'm currently watching the 6th Season and can't wait for the 7th Season to start.
